{"name":"Monitor stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Outlook 24/7","nodes":[{"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"minutes","minutesInterval":5}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"1345a990-76db-42a8-88f2-d50c40d13ccf","name":"Every Few Minutes"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://api.example.com/v1/metrics","options":{"timeout":20000},"sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"updated_since","value":"={{ $now.minus({hours: 6}).toISO() }}"},{"name":"limit","value":"100"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[54,400],"id":"5553916f-2594-47b5-97a5-4c22595b5a78","name":"Fetch Current Metrics","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Score each metric 0-100 from simple heuristics\nreturn $input.all().map(item => {\n  const j = item.json;\n  let score = 50;\n  if (j.kpi) score += 20;\n  if (j.value) score += 15;\n  if ((j.source || '') === 'referral') score += 15;\n  return { json: { ...j, score: Math.min(100, score) } };\n});"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[378,400],"id":"a90cf95f-1f9b-48b1-a5a5-51d34805f751","name":"Compute Severity Signals"},{"parameters":{"rules":{"values":[{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"e2ff9b46-9acf-4193-a486-5856007a6928","leftValue":"={{ $json.score ?? $json.momentum ?? 0 }}","rightValue":40,"operator":{"type":"number","operation":"lt"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"info"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"60482e34-1c3c-41db-bbf6-5491604d73a7","leftValue":"={{ $json.score ?? $json.momentum ?? 0 }}","rightValue":70,"operator":{"type":"number","operation":"gte"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"warning"},{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"19c81533-2d6f-4aea-b76a-7d4df615a002","leftValue":"={{ $json.score ?? $json.momentum ?? 0 }}","rightValue":90,"operator":{"type":"number","operation":"gte"}}],"combinator":"and"},"renameOutput":true,"outputKey":"critical"}]},"options":{"fallbackOutput":"extra"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.switch","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[702,400],"id":"e6962606-c1f2-4102-a7c2-5feab3e7cc0c","name":"Grade Severity Tier"},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1026,-80],"id":"e3456dd0-012a-46d1-8456-98d9e805c150","name":"Just Record (Info)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"subject":"=🟠 Warning tier reached: {{ $json.reportId }} at {{ $json.score ?? $json.last }}","bodyContent":"=🟠 Warning tier reached: {{ $json.reportId }} at {{ $json.score ?? $json.last }}","toRecipients":"={{ $json.email || 'ops@company.com' }}","additionalFields":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.microsoftOutlook","typeVersion":2,"position":[1350,400],"id":"4c7dc7c7-1841-424a-aedc-a2c74b08672d","name":"Warn Channel (Outlook)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#reporting","cachedResultName":"#reporting"},"text":"=🔴 CRITICAL: {{ $json.reportId }} breached threshold — act now","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[1674,880],"id":"25de319d-c088-4032-ba8d-e3b53f52584e","name":"Page Urgently (Slack)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Metric Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1998,1360],"id":"028ce03e-ea19-45f9-b799-25029a4bb2f6","name":"Archive Unscored","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[2646,400],"id":"5098089b-92b6-4401-9182-72e7226288b8","name":"Merge Tier Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Every Few Minutes\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — every 5 min. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Fetch Current Metrics","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"7a13bc1c-cf90-b987-5aef-b84a727dca35","name":"Note: Every Few Minutes"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Current Metrics\n\nGET https://api.example.com/v1/metrics — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nNext: Compute Severity Signals\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"7ff773be-f138-1a40-0bc4-b6362ab2935b","name":"Note: Fetch Current Metrics"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Compute Severity Signals\n\nCustom JavaScript: Score each metric 0-100 from simple heuristics\n\nNext: Grade Severity Tier","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"564f3e45-2eab-0838-fe94-0c195aa748dc","name":"Note: Compute Severity Signals"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Grade Severity Tier\n\nRoutes each item to one of 4 lanes: info, warning, critical + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Just Record (Info) · ②→ Warn Channel (Outlook) · ③→ Page Urgently (Slack) · ④→ Archive Unscored","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"0fb7d4d3-60d9-658d-0a9b-5773bca9d5ac","name":"Note: Grade Severity Tier"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Just Record (Info)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Tier Outcomes\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,40],"id":"9866a01d-a125-3ae7-556a-fa139af6aab8","name":"Note: Just Record (Info)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Warn Channel (Outlook)\n\nmicrosoftOutlook — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Tier Outcomes\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Microsoft OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"6ac5fc95-60b5-9df3-7bad-b8c7f5b9eded","name":"Note: Warn Channel (Outlook)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Page Urgently (Slack)\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Tier Outcomes\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,1000],"id":"0c6c7937-d2d7-11f7-efde-e6dd09f1d105","name":"Note: Page Urgently (Slack)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Archive Unscored\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Tier Outcomes\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,1480],"id":"28182e76-bbcd-f1a6-42f4-c038e0f02a4e","name":"Note: Archive Unscored"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Tier Outcomes\n\nRejoins 4 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"766abf34-76ce-d415-405d-3c7341b68f89","name":"Note: Merge Tier Outcomes"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Monitor stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Outlook 24/7\n\n**Pattern:** Threshold Monitoring · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nMonitor stock levels with HTTP / REST API and Outlook 24/7. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual exports is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nEvery Few Minutes → Fetch Current Metrics → Compute Severity Signals → Grade Severity Tier → Just Record (Info) → Merge Tier Outcomes\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to threshold monitoring without manual effort\n- Anyone automating exports in data\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; Google OAuth2 / service account; Microsoft OAuth2; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"ffec492d-efe5-1cc8-5900-7f24de2e271c","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your exports process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-500],"id":"1b3f8bdb-181c-db3b-1d0b-756b4e7a178e","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Every Few Minutes":{"main":[[{"node":"Fetch Current Metrics","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Current Metrics":{"main":[[{"node":"Compute Severity Signals","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Compute Severity Signals":{"main":[[{"node":"Grade Severity Tier","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Grade Severity Tier":{"main":[[{"node":"Just Record (Info)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Warn Channel (Outlook)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Page Urgently (Slack)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Archive Unscored","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Just Record (Info)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Warn Channel (Outlook)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Page Urgently (Slack)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Archive Unscored":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Tier Outcomes","type":"main","index":3}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"b2673600-73d7-46e5-88b0-d70a8bab1683","id":"FDX10217"}